        "product_desc_text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Nova Everyday Clutch isn't a mass-produced bag. It's a <strong>carefully designed accessory</strong> built around the specific realities of Indian women's lives — the heat, the travel, the back-to-back occasions, the need for something that works at a noon meeting and a 9pm dinner with no bag change in between.</p><p>Its dumpling silhouette — soft, rounded, structured — has a global sensibility but an unmistakably Indian ease. The bold woven stripes are designed to be a statement on their own, so the outfit around them doesn't need to try harder.</p>",
            "text_size": 17,
            "text_color": "#2d2d2d",
            "highlighted_text_color": "#000000",
            "highlighted_text_background": "#fcc947",
            "accent_text_color": "#f44336",
