        "craft_quality": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Handcrafted. Not Just a Word on a Tag.</h3><p>The woven crochet technique used in the Nova takes significantly longer than machine-stitching. Each stripe is built with tension-controlled weaving that gives the bag its signature plush, textured feel — the kind that people reach out to touch when they first see it.</p><p>Run your fingers across the surface and you'll understand immediately why this bag doesn't feel like anything else at this price. It doesn't feel synthetic. It doesn't feel like something that was made in 10 seconds on an assembly line. It feels <em>considered.</em></p>",
