            "text": "<h3>The Nova Promise — Zero-Risk Purchase</h3><p>We believe so strongly in the Nova that we've made buying it completely risk-free:</p><ul><li><strong>COD Available:</strong> You don't pay a rupee until the bag is physically in your hands at the door.</li><li><strong>7-Day Returns:</strong> Opened the box and feel it's not quite right? WhatsApp us. We'll arrange a free reverse-pickup from your home. No questions, no hold music.</li><li><strong>Quality Guarantee:</strong> If any craftsmanship issue appears within 90 days of purchase, we replace it. Full stop.</li></ul>",
