        "faq_section": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Your Questions, Answered Honestly</h3><p><strong>Q: Does COD really work for online orders?</strong><br>Yes — 100%. You place the order, our logistics partner delivers it to your pin code (27,000+ across India), and you pay in cash or UPI at the door. You can inspect the bag before paying.</p><p><strong>Q: How long does delivery take?</strong><br>Typically 3-5 business days. Metro cities (Mumbai, Delhi, Bengaluru, Hyderabad, Chennai) often receive within 2 days. You'll get a tracking link as soon as the order ships.</p><p><strong>Q: Will it fit my iPhone 15 Pro Max?</strong><br>Yes — tested it. Your phone with a standard case, a cardholder, keys, earphones, and basic cosmetics all fit with the kiss-lock clicking shut cleanly.</p><p><strong>Q: Is this really handmade or is that just marketing?</strong><br>The woven crochet technique is genuinely handcrafted. You'll feel the difference the moment you touch it — there's a subtle texture variation that machine-made bags can't replicate.</p><p><strong>Q: Can I return it if I don't like it?</strong><br>Absolutely. 7-day hassle-free returns. WhatsApp the order ID, we send a pickup to your door. No need to visit any post office or courier office.</p><p><strong>Q: Is it available in more colours?</strong><br>Yes — 10+ colour combinations available on the product page. New patterns added seasonally. Some colours sell out fast — check current availability.</p>",
