            "comments_title_size": 22,
            "comments_title_color": "#1a1a1a",
            "comment1_text": "I was so unsure about ordering online but the COD option made it easy. The bag arrived in 3 days. It's GORGEOUS. The texture is so rich — nothing like what I expected at this price. Already ordered the green-yellow one for my sister.",
