            "comment1_reply_likes": "12",
            "comment1_reply_timestamp": "10 min",
            "comment2_text": "Carried it to a work conference. Got three compliments from senior colleagues. One of them is a fashion blogger! She asked for the link. This bag punches 3x above its price.",
