            "comment2_reply_text": "That's the Nova effect! Thank you for sharing, Divya.",
            "comment2_reply_likes": "9",
            "comment2_reply_timestamp": "20 min",
            "comment3_text": "Bought 4 as Rakhi gifts — one for my mom, bhabhi, and two cousins. All four called me on the same day to say how beautiful it was. Best Rs.5,200 I've spent in a long time.",
