            "comment4_reply_text": "Thank you for the positive feedback! We're glad you're enjoying it.",
            "comment4_reply_likes": "5",
            "comment4_reply_timestamp": "1 h",
            "comment5_text": "Was hesitant because Rs.1,299 felt low for something that looks this good — I kept thinking there must be a catch. There is no catch. The quality is genuinely great. The stitching is tight, the closure clicks perfectly, and it feels light and durable. Already my most-reached-for bag.",
